    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gum prints combined with another process, typically platinum. The highlights and mid-tones are formed using a platinum print. A gum dichromate print is placed on top to enhance the shadow areas. Combination gum dichromate prints are rare.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
